Class EnrollStudent

java.lang.Object
src.EnrollStudent
public class EnrollStudent
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a student that is enrolled in the current semester. This class also contains important methods such as getters and setters and comparing functions.
Author:
Christian Osma, Liam Smith
